Token.Abstract:
Returns an MLModel that includes detailed metadata, and data source information as well as the current status of the MLModel.

GetMLModel provides results in normal or verbose format.

Parameter.Name: request
Parameter.Abstract: A container for the necessary parameters to execute the GetMLModel service method.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An instance of AWSTask. On successful execution, task.result will contain an instance of AWSMachineLearningGetMLModelOutput. On failed execution, task.error may contain an NSError with AWSMachineLearningErrorDomain domain and the following error code: AWSMachineLearningErrorInvalidInput, AWSMachineLearningErrorResourceNotFound, AWSMachineLearningErrorInternalServer.

Parameter.Name: request

Parameter.Name: completionHandler
Parameter.Abstract: The completion handler to call when the load request is complete. response - A response object, or nil if the request failed. error - An error object that indicates why the request failed, or nil if the request was successful. On failed execution, error may contain an NSError with AWSMachineLearningErrorDomain domain and the following error code: AWSMachineLearningErrorInvalidInput, AWSMachineLearningErrorResourceNotFound, AWSMachineLearningErrorInternalServer.

Token.Abstract:
Generates a prediction for the observation using the specified MLModel.

Note

Not all response parameters will be populated because this is dependent on the type of requested model.

Parameter.Name: request
Parameter.Abstract: A container for the necessary parameters to execute the Predict service method.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An instance of AWSTask. On successful execution, task.result will contain an instance of AWSMachineLearningPredictOutput. On failed execution, task.error may contain an NSError with AWSMachineLearningErrorDomain domain and the following error code: AWSMachineLearningErrorInvalidInput, AWSMachineLearningErrorResourceNotFound, AWSMachineLearningErrorLimitExceeded, AWSMachineLearningErrorInternalServer, AWSMachineLearningErrorPredictorNotMounted.
